<FilterBar
  filters={[
    {
      name: "chain",
      type: "select",
      label: "Chain",
      options: [
        { value: "", label: "All Chains" },
        { value: "Pharmacity", label: "Pharmacity" },
        { value: "SatraFood", label: "SatraFood" },
      ],
    },
    {
      name: "search",
      type: "text",
      label: "Search",
      placeholder: "Name, code, or address...",
    },
  ]}
  values={filters}
  onChange={(name, value) => setFilters((prev) => ({ ...prev, [name]: value }))}
/>
